props.name: text
props.description: Text to use within the breadcrumbs item. If content is provided in the default slot, this prop will be ignored.

props.name: href
props.description: Link for the breadcrumbs item. If not specified, breadcrumbs item is a normal list item.

props.name: component
props.description: The component used to render the link, for example `RouterLink`. Will default to `a` if an `href` is provided or no link otherwise.

slots.name: default
slots.description: The content of the breadcrumbs item. If content is provided in this slot, the `text` prop will be ignored.
